config PACKAGE_LIBS_PAM
	bool "pam"
	select PACKAGE_BUILD_TOOLS_FLEX
	select PACKAGE_DEVEL_FLEX
	select PACKAGE_LIBS_LIBTIRPC
	help
	  PAM (Pluggable Authentication Modules) is a system security tool
	  that allows system administrators to set authentication policy
	  without having to recompile programs that handle authentication.
